             was indicted for <rs id="t18080601-5-off21" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080601-5-off21" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080601-5-off21" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080601-5-cd22" type="crimeDate">25th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080601-5-off21 t18080601-5-cd22"></join>, in the dwelling house of 
                     <persName id="t18080601-5-victim82" type="victimName">
                        James 
                        Allardice
                     <interp inst="t18080601-5-victim82" type="surname" value="Allardice"></interp>
