                  , five shirts, value 50 s. a pair of breeches, value 10 s. four pair of stockings, value 10 s. a cap, value 2 s. five guineas, five bank notes, value 1 l. each, a bank note. value 5 l. and another bank note, value 20 l.
            </rs> the property of 
